{"type": "article", "id": 14339, "title": "Bear Papa 螺丝刀", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-03T07:12:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000306vGd12EY0uH4ltVa9.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这些呆萌的小熊竟是螺丝刀，而且功能非常齐全。拔出头部是一个完整的螺丝刀，腿部藏着六个不同型号的螺丝刀，它们可以相互替换以满足需要。小熊的头可以转动到不同位置，友好的外形让人顿生亲切感，放在家里既是装饰品，还非常安全。对于小孩来说，也是培养动手能力好机会。<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2015/09/01/unbearably-cute-tools/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141926D49JFpZOLirvle08.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"525\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141927EyFmIwGDz8pe4boK.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"700\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141927Yb8SZvfatKkDB12T.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"662\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.63047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}